sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Controller Manager
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KServe as KServe Router
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: TrustyAIService Reconciliation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch TrustyAIService CRs<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: TrustyAIService CR event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment (TrustyAI + OAuth)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Service + TLS Service<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route (TLS Passthrough)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token

    Note over Operator,ModelMesh: Flow 2: ModelMesh Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch ModelMesh Deployment<br/>(MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS env var)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    ModelMesh->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>80/TCP HTTP plaintext

    Note over Operator,KServe: Flow 3: KServe Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>(InferenceLogger spec)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    KServe->>TrustyAI: Inference data (InferenceLogger URL)<br/>80/TCP HTTP plaintext

    Note over User,TrustyAI: Flow 4: External User Access
    User->>Route: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS Passthrough
    Route->>OAuth: Forward<br/>8443/TCP TLS (serving cert)
    OAuth->>OAuth: OpenShift OAuth<br/>SAR check: pods/get
    OAuth->>TrustyAI: Authenticated request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP localhost
    TrustyAI-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Encrypted Response
    Route-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Prometheus,TrustyAI: Flow 5: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP plaintext
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir metrics
    Prometheus->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS / Bearer Token
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Operator metrics
